# CLOCK::ADVANCE_CLOCK_TIME_TO

## Summary
Advances the current time to the time specified

## Parameters
* **INT** h
* **INT** m
* **INT** s

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
if the new time is before the current time a day will pass on the date
